sql_query: SELECT      SALES_REP,     REGION,     SUM(BOOKING_REVENUE) AS TOTAL_BOOKING_REVENUE FROM      PENGUIN_INTELLIGENCE_HUB.GOLD.VW_KPI4_BOOKING_REVENUE_BY_SALESPERSON GROUP BY      SALES_REP, REGION ORDER BY      TOTAL_BOOKING_REVENUE DESC LIMIT 5;

prompt: give me top 5 sales person as per region
sql_query: WITH SalesRanking AS (   SELECT      s.SALES_REP,     s.SHIP_TO_REGION,     SUM(s.REVENUE) as TOTAL_REVENUE,     RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY s.SHIP_TO_REGION ORDER BY SUM(s.REVENUE) DESC) as REGION_RANK   FROM PENGUIN_INTELLIGENCE_HUB.GOLD.VW_KPI1_SALES_LEADER_BOARD s   WHERE s.SHIP_TO_REGION IS NOT NULL   GROUP BY s.SALES_REP, s.SHIP_TO_REGION ) SELECT    SALES_REP,   SHIP_TO_REGION,   TOTAL_REVENUE,   REGION_RANK FROM SalesRanking  WHERE REGION_RANK <= 5 ORDER BY SHIP_TO_REGION, REGION_RANK LIMIT 5

prompt: give me top 5 sales person as per region
sql_query: SELECT   t1.SALES_REP,   t1.REGION,   SUM(t1.SHIPMENT_REVENUE) AS total_revenue FROM   PENGUIN_INTELLIGENCE_HUB.GOLD.VW_KPI6_SHIPMENT_REVENUE_BY_SALESPERSON AS t1 GROUP BY   t1.SALES_REP,   t1.REGION ORDER BY   total_revenue DESC LIMIT 5;
